on of the University of Art and Design Linz as an internationally active hub of art, design, science and education.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tasks of the University of Art and Design Linz</strong></p>\r\n<p>The tasks of the University of Art and Design Linz arise from Art. 3 of the Universities Act of 2002, Federal Law Gazette I 2002/120 as amended.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1);
